 November 29, 2013 08:38 AM IST
Bay Capital sells 21.97 lakh shares of Westlife Development
On November 28, 2013 Bay Capital Investments Ltd sold 21,97,525 shares of Westlife Development at Rs 400 on the BSE.


 September 17, 2013 08:29 AM IST
Bay Capital sells 13 lakh shares of Westlife Development
On September 16, 2013 Bay Capital Investments Ltd sold 13,00,000 shares of Westlife Development at Rs 344.10 on the BSE.


 September 13, 2013 08:52 AM IST
Bay Capital sells 43.71 lakh shares of Westlife Development
On September 12, 2013 Bay Capital Investments Ltd sold 43,71,054 shares of Westlife Development at Rs 341 on the BSE. In the previous trading session, the share closed at Rs 330.80, down Rs 4.25, or 1.27 percent.






























